---
layout: layouts/base.liquid
title: Check for Affordable Housing Updates
permalink: 
  build: "/housing/affordable-housing/changes/index.html"
pageClass: "smaller"
maxUnits: 6
maxOfferings: 5
maxHouseholdSize: 12
---

